1
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,000
Miss Xiao.

2
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,440
Your Highness, you look much better.

3
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:05,000
It's all thanks to the medicine you brought me.

4
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,860
It was nothing.

5
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,539
But Your Highness, your body is too weak.

6
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:11,360
You must take good care of yourself from now on.

7
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,450
When I was seven,

8
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,120
I was poisoned.

9
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:16,840
Since then,

10
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,040
I've been recovering,

11
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,240
so I never had the chance to learn martial arts.

12
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,240
Miss Xiao, since you are skilled in martial arts...

13
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,320
What do you think I should learn?

14
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,610
I think Your Highness could learn archery

15
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:30,010
to protect yourself with external force.

16
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,810
Can you teach me?

17
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:46,400
I only came to deliver medicine to Your Highness.

18
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,240
Now that you have recovered,

19
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,660
I should return to the military camp.

20
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,200
Take care.

21
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,650
Your Majesty, your shoulder was injured by an arrow.

22
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,100
The injury is serious.

23
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,490
You shouldn't be drinking.

24
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,930
The palace is heavily guarded.

25
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,940
Why is he so badly injured?

26
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,320
His Majesty was afraid you would worry,

27
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,450
so he kept it from you

28
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,120
and wouldn't let me tell you.

29
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:25,720
There are unidentified assassins outside the palace.

30
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:26,760
His Majesty wouldn't let you leave the palace

31
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,090
in order to protect you.

32
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,520
Last time you left the palace,

33
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,400
His Majesty was worried about your safety,

34
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,660
so he followed you to the Xiao Residence.

35
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,120
A-Ling.

36
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,720
To protect you,

37
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,140
he got injured.

38
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,840
He did it to save me.

39
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,960
What happened to the Xiao family

40
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,760
was the work of these assassins.

41
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,700
But the Xiao family

42
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,570
was killed by assassins from the Xuanniao Tribe.

43
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:58,490
How do you know they were from the Xuanniao Tribe?

44
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,360
The Xuanniao Division was established by my Royal Father.

45
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,760
Few outsiders know of it.

46
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:14,960
I never expected someone

47
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:17,320
could pose as the Xuanniao Division to kill.

48
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:19,040
The totem of this fake division

49
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,160
is so detailed.

50
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,320
It differs from the real one

51
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,920
only by a hair on the tail feathers.

52
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,000
No wonder the Empress was mistaken.

53
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,680
Your Majesty.

54
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:37,240
The Empress has sought an audience several times.

55
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,880
She wants the truth.

56
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:41,520
Why not explain it to her?

57
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,720
With her misunderstanding of you,

58
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,200
I fear

59
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,290
more trouble may arise.

60
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,440
Pass on my order.

61
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,820
The Empress has behaved improperly.

62
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,060
She is to be confined to her quarters.

63
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,840
There are unidentified assassins outside the palace.

64
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,700
To protect you,

65
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,360
someone was injured.

66
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,880
What happened to the Xiao family

67
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,680
was the work of these assassins.

68
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,560
Why disguise themselves as the Xuanniao Tribe

69
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,090
to wipe out the Xiao family?

70
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,480
And why was Father

71
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,760
captured by Li Yunxi

72
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,120
and killed?

73
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:19,650
It's a pity Li Yunxi keeps avoiding me.

74
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,160
He refuses to see me.

75
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,560
Greetings, Consort Xue.

76
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,120
You are pregnant.

77
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,080
Since Your Majesty has noticed,

78
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,600
I won't hide it.

79
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,409
Then did you come here today

80
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,320
just to show off?

81
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,200
I came to ask

82
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:48,460
if you still want to leave the palace.

83
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,700
His Majesty killed General Xiao.

84
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,480
He murdered your father.

85
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,760
Do you really want to stay in the palace,

86
00:05:58,159 --> 00:06:00,440
act like a loving couple with His Majesty,

87
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,640
and live a lie?

88
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,080
But I am confined now.

89
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,060
Leaving the palace

90
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,650
will be even harder.

91
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,400
As long as you trust me,

92
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,720
I have a way.

93
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,400
Your Highness.

94
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,000
I heard Consort Xue is unwell

95
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,810
and won't attend the family banquet tonight.

96
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:31,400
Greetings, Your Majesty.

97
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,280
Your Majesty.

98
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:49,040
Consort Xue's pregnancy is a great joy.

99
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,659
Let me propose a toast.

100
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,290
Let me pour you another cup.

101
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,880
Your clothes are wet.

102
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,240
Your Majesty,

103
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,000
let me help you change.

104
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:35,880
So clumsy.

105
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,800
I'll get changed.

106
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,640
I'm done.

107
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:46,850
I'm leaving.

108
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,960
Give me back my jade pendant.

109
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,800
This is my jade pendant.

110
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,060
My mother gave it to me.

111
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,530
You gave it to me,

112
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,480
so it's mine.

113
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,880
I regret it now.

114
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:05,780
Give it back right now.

115
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,210
What's mine is mine.

116
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,500
No one can take it away.

117
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,820
Why are you making such a fuss?

118
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,680
Forget it.

119
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,560
If you like it,

120
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,380
you can have it.

121
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:22,920
You...

122
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,130
still care about me,

123
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,040
don't you?

124
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:48,300
Never mind.

125
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:52,480
Let this jade pendant keep you company in my stead.

126
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,680
Why didn't Your Grace leave

127
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,940
at the time agreed upon with Consort Xue?

128
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,800
I cannot trust her completely,

129
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,240
so we need to leave the palace early.

130
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:13,840
So Your Grace is guarding against Consort Xue.

131
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,050
Hanxing.

132
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,290
Hanxing.

133
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,320
Hanxing's shoes.

134
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:02,280
Hanxing.

135
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:04,880
Hanxing.

136
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:07,600
Hanxing.

137
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,920
Why do I feel so weak?

138
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:18,330
When was I drugged with Soft Muscle Powder again?

139
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:22,680
Li Yunxi.

140
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,300
Why on earth do you want to kill me?

141
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:27,640
Wait, no.

142
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:30,160
This isn't Li Yunxi's jade pendant.

143
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:31,680
Who is it?

144
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,130
Who wants to kill me?

145
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:02,560
Empress.

146
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:06,560
You must hate His Majesty until you die.

147
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:12,520
Don't come looking for His Majesty even as a ghost.

148
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,960
That way, His Majesty can be mine forever.

149
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,040
So,

150
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,680
it was you sending me the message

151
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:36,480
that the Empress was leaving the palace early.

152
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,080
Your Majesty,

153
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:50,360
you must hate His Majesty until the day you die.

154
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:52,240
So it was you who sent me word

155
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,640
that the Empress had left the palace early.

156
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,520
Have I been reborn again?
